        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-92b240f3-7634-4bce-a65a-426a42c2a5ce">
                The Chancellor of the Exchequer (Mr. Gaitskell)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-92b240f3-7634-4bce-a65a-426a42c2a5ce" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
