        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-886a5260-4316-49e1-9a8c-a74707686cf6">
                Mr. Churchill
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-886a5260-4316-49e1-9a8c-a74707686cf6" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1951-06-28/debates/ea57909d-d5fe-40e5-a45e-eb4ad4d695c6/Metals(AllocationScheme)#contribution-886a5260-4316-49e1-9a8c-a74707686cf6">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">On a point of order. If Questions are to be selected which have not been reached in the ordinary course might not some consideration be given to Question No. 45, addressed to the Prime Minister?<p></p> [Mr. HOLLIS,—<em>To ask the Prime Minister, whether the speech of the Minister of Supply at Margate on 21st June, to the effect that drastic action would be taken against the Iron and Steel Federation if the Federation refused to the Iron and Steel Corporation effective control of purchase of iron ore abroad, represented the policy of the Government.</em>]</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-886a5260-4316-49e1-9a8c-a74707686cf6" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1951-06-28/debates/ea57909d-d5fe-40e5-a45e-eb4ad4d695c6/Metals(AllocationScheme)#contribution-886a5260-4316-49e1-9a8c-a74707686cf6">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
